      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Convert a LearnDash Website to Mobile Apps for iOS and Android</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Want to build a LearnDash app from your site? There's only one option that really makes sense - find out more in our guide!</p>
